long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
ShareComment is a Chrome extension designed for adding comments, notes, annotations to open-source projects on GitHub. 

It can simplify, enhance the process of providing feedback and engaging in YOUR CODE IDEA among all developers.

ShareComment facilitates seamless sharing of ideas, suggestions, and opinions, thereby improving project quality and fostering interaction within the open-source community.
